                     <interp inst="t18220109-58-person594" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a watchman. I assisted in securing the prisoner.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18220109-58-person595">
                  SAMUEL 
                  HILL
               <interp inst="t18220109-58-person595" type="surname" value="HILL"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18220109-58-person595" type="given" value="SAMUEL"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18220109-58-person595" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . The prisoner was brought to the watch-house. I found three duplicates of the property produced,<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="182201090033"></xptr>on him, and the key which unlocked the door of Miss Watson's plate closet.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner. I leave it entirely to your Lordship.</p>
               <p>GUILTY - Aged 42.</p>
               <p>Of <rs id="t18220109-58-verdict291" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18220109-58-verdict291" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18220109-58-verdict291" type="verdictSubcategory" value="theftunder40s"></interp>
               stealing to the value of 39 s. only
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>
